	* libgnomevfs-corba/Makefile.am: Don't use `GNOME_CFLAGS'.

2000-05-08  Pavel Cisler  <pavel@eazel.com>

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-xfer.c:
	(system_time):
	Fix it to return a correct value.
	
