	`GNOME_VFS_FILE_INFO_NOOPTION' to `GNOME_VFS_FILE_INFO_DEFAULT'.
	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-xfer.c (create_xfer_file_list): Updated
	accordingly.

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-uri.c (gnome_vfs_uri_extract_dirname): New
	function.

